# Attack 08 – Ransomware Simulation

## Objective

Simulate ransomware behaviour in an isolated lab.

## Attack

Executed a harmless ransomware simulation to generate file modification activity.

## Detection

Wazuh monitored suspicious file activity and process execution.

## MITRE ATT&CK

- T1486 – Data Encrypted for Impact

## Investigation

Reviewed file creation, process activity, and endpoint telemetry.

## Outcome

Simulation successfully generated security events for analysis.
